OL,3,CGas prices soar as Qatar halts
OL,4,Cproduction after Iranian strikes
OL,6,FGas prices have leapt at the fastest
OL,7,Fpace since the outbreak of war in
OL,8,FUkraine, after Iranian strikes led
OL,9,FQatar to halt production of liquified
OL,10,Fnatural gas.
OL,12,FOil prices also soared and global
OL,13,Ffinancial markets reeled from the
OL,14,Ffallout of an intensifying conflict
OL,15,Fbetween Iran and US-Israeli forces.
OL,17,FEuropean whole gas prices soared by
OL,18,F52% on Monday, marking the sharpest
OL,19,Frise since prices were pushed
OL,20,Fdramatically higher by the Russian
OL,21,Finvasion of Ukraine in March 2022.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G1/7
