OL,3,CGas prices soar as Qatar halts
OL,4,Cproduction after Iranian strikes
OL,6,FThe surge came after Qatar's state-
OL,7,Fbacked energy company QatarEnergy said
OL,8,Fit "ceased production" because of
OL,9,Fattacks on its facilities.
OL,11,FQatari ministers had said earlier on
OL,12,FMonday that an Iranian drone had
OL,13,Fattacked one of the company's
OL,14,Fproduction facilities.
OL,16,FQatar is a major producer of LNG,
OL,17,Fcooled gas which can be transported
OL,18,Fvia ships, responsible for about a
OL,19,Ffifth of global supplies.
OL,26,@pD@DOUpD@VO]
