OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F313A1772478696
OL,3,CGas prices soar as Qatar halts
OL,4,Cproduction after Iranian strikes
OL,6,FOn Monday in London, the price of
OL,7,Fnatural gas for delivery in April was
OL,8,Fup by about 43% to 115p per therm.
OL,10,FIn the UK, gas prices are a key driver
OL,11,Ffor the cost of domestic energy bills,
OL,12,Findicating that a sustained spike
OL,13,Fcould affect households in the coming
OL,14,Fmonths.
OL,16,FNeil Wilson, Saxo UK investor
OL,17,Fstrategist, said: "Qatar is a top
OL,18,Fthree LNG exporter, controlling
OL,19,Froughly a quarter of expected supply
OL,20,Fover the next decade.
OL,26,@yD@SOU
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G3/7
