OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F313A1772478696
OL,3,CGas prices soar as Qatar halts
OL,4,Cproduction after Iranian strikes
OL,6,F"Looks like Iran's tactic is to
OL,7,Fpressure Gulf states so they in turn
OL,8,Fpressure the US and Israel to back
OL,9,Foff."
OL,11,FGlobal financial markets faltered
OL,12,Fafter intense strikes across the
OL,13,FMiddle East, and attacks on ships
OL,14,Fdrove fears of energy supply
OL,15,Fdisruption.
OL,17,FOil supplies could be affected by the
OL,18,Fconflict after Iran reportedly warned
OL,19,Ftankers on the Strait of Hormuz that
OL,20,Fno ships would be allowed to pass
OL,21,Fthrough.
OL,26,@nD@AOU
