OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F313A1772478696
OL,3,CGas prices soar as Qatar halts
OL,4,Cproduction after Iranian strikes
OL,6,FUK Maritime Trade Operations Centre
OL,7,Fofficials said that two vessels have
OL,8,Fbeen struck near the key trade artery.
OL,10,FThe Strait of Hormuz is used by
OL,11,Ftankers carrying about one-fifth of
OL,12,Fthe world's oil supplies and seaborne
OL,13,Fgas.
OL,15,FOn Monday, the price of Brent crude
OL,16,Foil soared by as much as 13%, rising
OL,17,Fabove $82 (#61) a barrel, before
OL,18,Ffalling back.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G5/7
