OL,3,CGas prices soar as Qatar halts
OL,4,Cproduction after Iranian strikes
OL,6,FSubscribe free to our weekly
OL,7,Fnewsletter for exclusive and original
OL,8,Fcoverage from ITV News. Direct to your
OL,9,Finbox every Friday morning.
OL,11,FThe conflict has also heavily impacted
OL,12,Fthe stock market, with tourism
OL,13,Fbusinesses and airlines seeing the
OL,14,Fshaprest declines.
OL,16,FCruise giant Carnival slid by 8%,
OL,17,Fwhile airline firm IAG, the parent
OL,18,Ffirm of British Airways, dipped by
OL,19,F7.6%.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G6/7
