OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F313A1772478696
OL,3,CGas prices soar as Qatar halts
OL,4,Cproduction after Iranian strikes
OL,6,FWizz Air, which typically runs flights
OL,7,Fto Dubai and Abu Dhabi, was also down
OL,8,F7.3% in early trading on Monday, while
OL,9,Ftravel-focused retail groups SSP and
OL,10,FWH Smith were also lower.
OL,12,FHowever, defence stocks were among the
OL,13,Fgainers, with BAE Systems lifting by
OL,14,F7.4%.
